        "simple-intro-text": "This website uses cookies to improve your browsing experience and make it faster and more interactive. \n\nThis cookie policy describes the cookies used and explains how to enable or disable them. We invite you to periodically check the content of this page, together with the privacy policy available on our website, to stay up to date with any changes we may make.",
